<br />

<br />
Wisdom? Why on earth wisdom? I put my points in STA and INT on creation, and I'm an all around bard (vah shir, both solo and group). I think it's a bad choice to place your stats solely on the assumption that you're either gonna solo or group, because you WILL do both.</span></td>
