			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: All Bards are not created equal, a Bards take on creation.<a name="40230"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">May 17 04 9:50 AM</span></td>
